<div class="info my-10">
    <div class="top flex justify-between">
        <div class="post flex flex-col gap-2">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold">
                <%= property.title %>
            </h1>
            <div class="address flex gap-1 items-center text-[#888]">
                <LuMapPin />
                <span>
                    <%= property.address %>
                </span>
            </div>
            <div class="address flex gap-1 items-center text-[#555]">
                <span>Posted by: <%= property.author.username %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="price text-lg font-light py-2 px-3 bg-[#ffe6a7] w-fit rounded-md">
                $ <%= property.price %>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="user flex px-12 flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 bg-[#f0ebd8] rounded-md font-semibold">
            <svg class="h-12 w-12 text-gray-300" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd"
                    d="M18.685 19.097A9.723 9.723 0 0021.75 12c0-5.385-4.365-9.75-9.75-9.75S2.25 6.615 2.25 12a9.723 9.723 0 003.065 7.097A9.716 9.716 0 0012 21.75a9.716 9.716 0 006.685-2.653zm-12.54-1.285A7.486 7.486 0 0112 15a7.486 7.486 0 015.855 2.812A8.224 8.224 0 0112 20.25a8.224 8.224 0 01-5.855-2.438zM15.75 9a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0z"
                    clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
                <span>
                <%= property.author.username %>
            </span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bottom text-[#555] mt-10 leading-relaxed">
        <%= property.description %>
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Error magnam qui eius tenetur, dolorem similique
            suscipit laudantium quia ut ex, soluta iusto debitis fugit aut, consectetur distinctio quo animi
            reprehenderit?
    </div>
</div>